        "content": "### 1. Trigger, Data Fetch & Jira Issue Convert\n\n* **Schedule Trigger:** Triggers the workflow execution at the defined frequency.\n* **Fetch Worklogs:** Retrieves data from the `DailyWorkLog` Airtable table.\n* **Jira Issue Convert:** Transforms the user-friendly **`Issue Key`** into the **`Issue ID`**."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
